# Accessibility

- WCAG 2.1 Level AA compliance. Not optional.
- Keyboard navigable (Tab, Enter, Escape, arrows). ARIA live regions for hints. Proper roles (`tooltip`, `dialog`).
- Focus management: hint appears → focus moves. Dismissed → focus returns.
- Color contrast 4.5:1. Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` and `prefers-color-scheme`.
- All images/icons have alt text or aria-label.
- Run axe-core in CI. Keyboard-only E2E tests. Screen reader testing before major releases.
